ai-patthana16.93:0.2_0: Having given the immaculateness of the Dhamma
ai-patthana16.93:0.3_0: Talking for oneself, looking for support,
ai-patthana16.93:1.1_0: Not being visible and without impingement. Consciousness doesn’t give rise to dependence on repulsion.
ai-patthana16.93:2.1_0: One who has not attended on repulsion towards the goal of exertion, nor does repulsion come to be.
ai-patthana16.93:2.1_2: There are three more mendicants who have no regrets.
